            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for increasing the yield of phellinus igniarius secondary metabolites by using a black fungus chaff extracting solution, which comprises the following steps of: firstly, culturing phellinus igniarius strains by using a phellinus igniarius liquid culture medium with a relatively low carbon nitrogen ratio and a pH (Potential of Hydrogen) which is most suitable for the growth of the phellinus igniarius strains; growth of phellinus igniarius mycelia, large-amount accumulation of secondary metabolites such as polysaccharide, flavone and polyphenol in the mycelia and small-amount accumulation of triterpenes are promoted; along with the growth of phellinus igniarius hyphae, the pH value of the whole culture medium is continuously reduced, at the moment, accumulation of triterpenes is not facilitated, so that a new nitrogen source ammonium nitrate is added into the phellinus igniarius liquid culture medium, under the stress of low-concentration CO, the pH value is increased, and rapid accumulation of triterpenes is promoted under the combined action of CO stimulation, the new nitrogen source and the high pH value; according to the method, the yield of four secondary metabolites of polysaccharide, flavone, polyphenol and triterpene can be greatly increased at the same time, the operation process is simple, and practicability is high."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了利用黑木耳菌糠提取液提升桑黄次生代谢产物产量的方法，首先用较低碳氮比的桑黄液体培养基以及最适宜桑黄菌种生长的pH来培养桑黄菌种，同时由于桑黄液体培养基中添加有黑木耳菌糠提取液，促进了桑黄菌丝体生长以及菌丝体中次生代谢产物多糖、黄酮、多酚的大量累积以及三萜的少量累积；而随着桑黄菌丝的生长整个培养基的pH不断降低，此时更不利于三萜的累积，因此向桑黄液体培养基中加入新的氮源硝酸铵和在低浓度的CO胁迫下，并调高pH，在CO刺激和新的氮源和高pH的共同作用下促进三萜的快速累积；本发明能够同时大幅度提高多糖、黄酮、多酚和三萜四种次生代谢物产量，操作过程简单，实用性强。"
                }
            ]
